{"tid":1359292,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【爆相爆片】網紅「娘娘」杜小喬收兵 秘撻大台藝員仔譚永浩","createTime":"2019-07-24T06:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T08:04:55.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1bdf801366ad04ae4cb9db6b5f41adc8ae197055","tid":1359292,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:02:23.000Z","msg":"杜小喬與無綫藝人譚永浩演音樂劇撻着 戲假情真男友IG大方認愛<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190724/59823528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190724%2F59823528&d=WWcUXgYU4baXfieBSZbTe7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=4bb1518e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190724%2F59823528&h=f10218fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190724/59823528</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/vdo/20190723/720pix/1563878784_1079.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2Fvdo%2F20190723%2F720pix%2F1563878784_1079.jpg&h=ccf45934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n29歲網絡女神「娘娘」杜小喬，曾被傳收兵無數的她，自爆初戀發生在13歲，至今只拍過兩次拖，一次長達9年，一次差唔多1年；而dry了3年的她，原來已靜靜地又收兵，日前杜小喬和新歡在灣仔街頭拖手仔，被讀者Yiu透過「爆相爆片」分享，更認出她的新歡是大台藝員仔&mdash;&mdash;譚永浩。"},{"pid":"29d8a75db75bf4fbc715a539338e947fd9b6d1d0","tid":1359292,"uid":233316,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:03:43.000Z","msg":"咁猛太陽仲出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b48c848cfc6c80a04780114fded1ea52dc011d","tid":1359292,"uid":85180,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181121/720pix/21ec3p1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2